reviewText: Incomplete instructions in  videos. The instructor doesn't explain huge lines of code and just skips through them by just reading them.  They assume we know everything and just read the code. Skip explaining lots of parts. Makes this course very confusing. This has to be remade by putting more thought into it.
It was so easy to pass this course. Thank you for the certificate. Some videos were informative.
For a very good start towards AWS Containers learning and understanding!
I​t' really a nice course and give intuitive into the containerized applications

Great course very well done. Useful to understand more of AWS services that manage containers, like ECS, EKS, Lambda, AppRunner and more. The exercises may use some AWS credit, but are very useful and very well written. I reccomend this course
Thank you instructors for share your knowledge on containers, kubernetes and others services da aws.
Excellent course to get into touch with Containerized applications.
A must learn course for all those folks who are amateur with container services and applications in AWS
